{
  "title": "node inspector",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.7em; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\">如果你在编写Node.js代码，node-inspector是必备之选，比Node.js的内置调试器好出许多。使用起来跟Chrome的javascript调试器很相似。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.7em; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\">使用npm安装：</font></p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"line-height: 22px; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 0px 15px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; margin: 20px -10px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px 0px; border-style: none; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><code style=\"font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"pln\">$ npm install </span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">g node</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">inspector</span></font></code></pre><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.7em; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\">然后需要通过浏览器连接到node-inspector，需要启动inspector服务：</font></p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"line-height: 22px; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 0px 15px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; margin: 20px -10px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-width: 1px 0px; border-style: none; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><code style=\"font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"pln\">$ node</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">inspector </span><span class=\"pun\">&amp;</span></font></code></pre><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.7em; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\">最后以debug模式运行node.js应用：</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.7em; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\">$ node </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\">--</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\">debug app</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\">.</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;\">js</span></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.7em; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\">通过URL <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/debug?port=5858\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">http://127.0.0.1:8080/debug?port=5858</a> 就可以进行调试了。</font></p>"
    }
  ]
}